{"id": "art-2435", "label": "Art. 2435", "title": "Art. 2435", "slug": "art-2435", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_60591499\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1786\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_60591499\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 243<sup>5</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_237112511\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1785\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_237112511\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>În cazul în care fuziunea prin <span class=SpellE>absorb&#355;ie</span>\neste realizat&#259; de o societate absorbant&#259; care <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span>\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 90%, dar nu totalitatea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>/<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau a altor valori mobiliare ce confer&#259; titularilor lor drept de\nvot în adun&#259;rile generale ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>,\nnu este necesar&#259; elaborarea rapoartelor prev&#259;zute la art. 243<sup>2</sup>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 243<sup>3</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nîndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> privind informarea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. 244 alin. (1) lit. b), d) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ne). Articolul 242 alin. (3) r&#259;mâne aplicabil.</span></p>"}